Key Match Events: Woakes took the final wicket of Rauf.
Stokes took three catches in the innings.
Post-Match Reflections: Willey expressed disappointment about the overall tournament performance but was pleased with his personal milestone of 100 ODI wickets.

Miscellaneous Highlights: The match was held at Eden Gardens, Kolkata.
